summary: Adjustment Monochromatic and Sepia tone  ENB.
descriptionHtml:
Adjustment Monochromatic ENB.
Possible to the Sepia tone in the enbpalette.bmp of options.

include 3 version,1 opition.

install
-------------
Choose one of them to your like.

 - Colorize
	Colorize and adjustment \"Monochrome ENB\" .

 - Monochrome
	\"Monochrome ENB\".

 - Noise
	Add Film grain effect to \"Monochrome ENB\".

 - Optional Sepia enbpalette
	Sepia tone enbpalette.bmp. Use it to overwrite.
===
